org.codice.ddf.resourcemanagement.query.plugin

Class ActiveSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.resourcemanagement.query.plugin.ActiveSearch

  • public class ActiveSearch
extends Object
    ActiveSearch provides relevant data pertaining to a search that is currently active (a search that has not yet completed). Includes the client information String, CQL query String, start time of the search Date, source being searched Source, and uniqueID UUID
